ext-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Delicious base recipe. I added a drained tin of green lentils instead of mushrooms as my kids aren’t fond of them. Will definitely repeat as there were cries for more and empty plates all round. Served with cheese mash.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-1035191"><a id="comment-1035191"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"><div class="user-picture"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/avatar/public/pictures/picture-6178951-1512213793.jpg?itok=r7HnkQ2D" width="40" height="40" alt="Trudie Chris&#039;s picture" title="Trudie Chris&#039;s picture" /></div></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">Trudie Chris</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 11th Jan, 2018</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">3.8</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">I used smoked cured ham cubes and replaced the stock and vinegar with white wine as well.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-1014966"><a id="comment-1014966"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><d